node.text: Very hyped on these @amazfit.us headphones! They fit very well and don’t fly out of my ears when I skate, have noise cancelling abilities up to 40dB, water resistant, all around killer headphones! Link in bio if you want to get yourself a pair 🎧🎶 #amazfit #TRexPro #SportsWatch #FitnessTracker #AmazfitSmartWatch #MilitaryWatch #PowerBudsPro #Earbuds #ad
